<p>This document specifies the standardized TextSample JSONL format used th=
roughout the GigaCheck system for both classification and detection tasks. =
All training and evaluation data must conform to this format. The standardi=
zed format enables consistent data processing across diverse source dataset=
s and supports both task types from a common schema.</p>
<p>For information about loading specific datasets into this format, see <a=
 href=3D"https://deepwiki.com/ai-forever/gigacheck/3.2-classification-datas=
et-loaders" class=3D"text-neutral-300 hover:text-neutral-200 hover:underlin=
e">Classification Dataset Loaders</a> and <a href=3D"https://deepwiki.com/a=
i-forever/gigacheck/3.3-detection-dataset-loaders" class=3D"text-neutral-30=
0 hover:text-neutral-200 hover:underline">Detection Dataset Loaders</a>. Fo=
r training pipeline requirements, see <a href=3D"https://deepwiki.com/ai-fo=
rever/gigacheck/4-training" class=3D"text-neutral-300 hover:text-neutral-20=
0 hover:underline">Training</a>.</p>
