/code>, <code class=3D"rounded-sm bg-[#e5e5e5] px-[0.25rem] py-[0.20rem] te=
xt-xs font-normal leading-[15px] before:hidden after:hidden dark:bg-[#48484=
8]/30">"mistral"</code>, etc.</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><strong>text</strong>: Content field with the following constraints:
<ul>
<li>Minimum length enforced during training (default: 100 characters, confi=
gurable via <code class=3D"rounded-sm bg-[#e5e5e5] px-[0.25rem] py-[0.20rem=
] text-xs font-normal leading-[15px] before:hidden after:hidden dark:bg-[#4=
84848]/30">--min_sequence_length</code>)</li>
<li>Maximum length enforced via truncation (default: 1024 tokens, configura=
ble via <code class=3D"rounded-sm bg-[#e5e5e5] px-[0.25rem] py-[0.20rem] te=
xt-xs font-normal leading-[15px] before:hidden after:hidden dark:bg-[#48484=
8]/30">--max_sequence_length</code>)</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><strong>data_type</strong>: Domain identifier to enable domain-aware tr=
aining and evaluation</li>
</ul>
