<p>The TextSample JSONL format provides a unified, extensible schema for bo=
th classification and detection tasks in the GigaCheck system. Its design e=
nables:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Consistency</strong>: All datasets conform to the same core str=
ucture</li>
<li><strong>Extensibility</strong>: Task-specific fields extend the core wi=
thout breaking compatibility</li>
<li><strong>Efficiency</strong>: JSONL format supports streaming and parall=
el processing</li>
<li><strong>Flexibility</strong>: Supports binary/ternary classification an=
d fine-grained interval detection</li>
</ul>
<p>All dataset loaders output this format, and all training scripts consume=
 it, creating a standardized pipeline from raw data to trained models.</p>
